%^ORANGE%^ULINE%^Orc Bloodline%^RESET%^

The rage of your ancestors burns within you, and the taint of savage orc blood flows through your veins. Your anger is never far from the surface, giving you strength and driving you to seek greater power.

%^ORANGE%^Bloodline Arcana:%^RESET%^
When you cast a damaging spell, that spell gains bonus damage based on your charisma.

%^ORANGE%^Warlord Reborn (L31):%^RESET%^
You inherit the resilience of an orcish warlord ancestor. You gain scaling fire resistance percent of 10 + sorcerer level and +5 damage resistance. 

%^ORANGE%^Bonus Bloodline Skill%^RESET%^: survival

%^ORANGE%^Bonus Spells%^RESET%^: burning hands, scorcher, fireball, wall of fire, cloudkill, tar pool, delayed blast fireball, iron body, meteor swarm
